name: MWG
description: There are approximately over 200 billion stars in the Milky Way Galaxy. The Milky Way Foundation, in collaboration with numerous global communities, has created the Defi3.0 Galaxy Coin (MWG), with a total circulation of 100000 coins. Each coin represents over 2 million stars, and each coin is extremely precious. MWG, based on the Defi faith, emerged as a masterpiece of the ages and is a flower of God that adheres to mathematical principles. The MWG adheres to the core concept of decentralization, Building a digital ecological platform based on core value scales and economic models, and based on the principles of value creation and fair distribution of value, the birth of Galaxy Coin aims to become a leader and industry benchmark in the Defi field, becoming the Bitcoin in the Defi field.
